en_7545763_0	Colombo (News 1st): Two Chinese nationals have been arrested in a hotel in Colpetty with a machine used to forge credit cards.
en_7545763_1	Police have also seized 5 blank cards used for printing credit cards and a laptop.
en_7545763_2	The suspects were arrested following a tip-off received from the Police Narcotics Bureau.
en_7545763_3	The two suspects along with the seized items have been handed over to the Criminal Investigations Department for further investigations.
